  "theme": "Write about things you find strong or weak, a personal challenge you worked hard at, and the power of studying.",
  "prompts": [
    {
      "prompt": "Open your composition by introducing yourself and describing what kind of person you are. Are you strong-minded or sometimes timid? Use 強気 or 弱気.",
